txt.en: 'Where is it that you come from?'
Register your heritage with the notary.

'Ah... Lindon.\n\n'You hail from Lindon, the green lands of the Elves between Ered Luin and the Sea, where Gil-galad, the last great Elf-king, once ruled. Círdan the Shipwright now rules there from Mithlond, the Grey Havens.'
